Package uz.pdp.quizService.uml

Interface BaseClass

All Known Implementing Classes:
Answer, Question, Role, User
public interface BaseClass
Marker interface for domain models in the application.

Classes implementing this interface are considered part of the application's core domain (such as User, Question, Answer).

Possible use cases:

  • Providing a common type hierarchy for domain entities.
  • Allowing special handling of all domain models via reflection.
  • Future extension with shared fields (id, createdAt, etc.).
